"title": "5413: money, attitudes to",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5413",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Money can be a blessing or a snare according to one's attitude.</p>\n<h2>Money as a gift from God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:18\">DEU 8:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:7\">1SA 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs3:13\">1KI 3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:18-Prov8:21\">PRO 8:18–8:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></p>\n<h2>The dangers of money</h2>\n<h3>Being ruled by money</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:24\">MAT 6:24</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:13\">LUK 16:13</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:5\">EPH 5:5</a></p>\n<h3>Loving money</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:10\">1TI 6:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl5:10\">ECC 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:14\">LUK 8:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:14\">LUK 16:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:3\">1TI 3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:8\">1TI 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:2\">2TI 3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:7\">TIT 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:5\">HEB 13:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:2\">1PE 5:2</a></p>\n<h3>Trusting in money</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:12-Deut8:14\">DEU 8:12–8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job31:24\">JOB 31:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps52:7\">PSA 52:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:10\">PSA 62:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:4\">PRO 11:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:28\">PRO 11:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:24\">PRO 27:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa10:3\">ISA 10:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:7\">JER 48:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:16-Luke12:21\">LUK 12:16–12:21</a> <em>the parable of the rich fool</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:11\">JAS 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:1-Jas5:3\">JAS 5:1–5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:14\">REV 18:14</a></p>\n<h3>Boasting in money</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:5-Ps49:6\">PSA 49:5–49:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:23-Jer9:24\">JER 9:23–9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:8\">HOS 12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:13-Jas4:16\">JAS 4:13–4:16</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of those led astray by the love of money</h2>\n<p>Balaam:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut23:4\">DEU 23:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:15\">2PE 2:15</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh7:20-Josh7:21\">JOS 7:20–7:21</a> <em>Achan</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:19-2Kgs5:27\">2KI 5:19–5:27</a> <em>Gehazi</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:22-Matt19:23\">MAT 19:22–19:23</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:22-Mark10:23\">MRK 10:22–10:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:23-Luke18:24\">LUK 18:23–18:24</a> <em>the rich young ruler</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:14-Matt26:15\">MAT 26:14–26:15</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:10-Mark14:11\">MRK 14:10–14:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:4-Luke22:5\">LUK 22:4–22:5</a> <em>Judas Iscariot</em></p>\n<h2>Gifts and qualities that are better than money</h2>\n<h3>Redemption</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:7-Ps49:9\">PSA 49:7–49:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa52:3\">ISA 52:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:26\">MAT 16:26</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:37\">MRK 8:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:25\">LUK 9:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:18-1Pet1:19\">1PE 1:18–1:19</a></p>\n<h3>Wisdom</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov4:7\">PRO 4:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps49:20\">PSA 49:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:13-Prov3:16\">PRO 3:13–3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov8:10-Prov8:11\">PRO 8:10–8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:16\">PRO 16:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:16\">PRO 17:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov20:15\">PRO 20:15</a></p>\n<h3>A good reputation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:1\">PRO 22:1</a></strong></p>\n<h3>A good wife</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:10\">PRO 31:10</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Healing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:6\">ACT 3:6</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Spiritual power</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:19-Acts8:20\">ACT 8:19–8:20</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Spiritual riches</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:1\">ISA 55:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev3:18\">REV 3:18</a></p>",
